# [ ] Create Google OAuth credentials
# [ ] Add authorized redirect URIs in Google Console
# [ ] Copy GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID and GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET
# [ ] Test authentication locally
# [ ] Update NEXTAUTH_URL for production deployment
